determination, work ethic, and talent that made possible a championship season also surely
bode well for their future success; these young men have inspired their community and serve as
exceptional ambassadors of the State of Tennessee; now, therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE ONE HUNDRED
FOURTEENTH GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, THE SENATE
CONCURRING, that we honor and congratulate the Unity School Lions boys' basketball team
upon winning the 2025 TMSAA Class A state championship, salute these exceptional student-
athletes for their many accomplishments, both on and off the court, and extend to them our best
wishes for much continued success in all their future endeavors.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, that an appropriate copy of this resolution be prepared
for presentation with this final clause omitted from such copy and upon proper request made to
the appropriate clerk, the language appearing immediately following the State seal appear
without House or Senate designation.
